snippet.title: Longplay - Rayman (Atari Jaguar | HD 720p60)
snippet.description:
My  Birthday-Special for my YouTube channel :)

My redo of my old Longplay, is my special gift for my great community ♥

The main Gameplay is 5 hours long! :o 
So what could the remaining 33 mins be? ;) Specials! Bonus! Demos! :D... I've played a little bit of the Ray Breakout Mini-Game, I showed you all the Demo videos of the game :) and! I showed you the developer messages! :D 
I hope you are going to enjoy this video! ♥

Credits: 5:01:40
Ray Breakout Mini-Game: 5:04:37
All Demo-Videos: 5:11:50
Developer Messages: 5:28:40

I've made the developer-messages on double speed because, some of them are really long...and I don't want my video to be 6hours long or so x'D lol
anyway, if someone of you understands French, please feel free to translate it for all of us :)

---
My old Longplay: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I6G-nPycfnU
Thanks for watching :)
---
Name of the Game: Rayman 1
From Year: 1995
Genre: Jump 'n' Run
Game by: Ubi Soft Entertainment
System: Atari Jaguar 
(Also on Systems like PC [MS DOS], Play Station 1, Sega Saturn, GameBoy Advance, GameBoy Color and NintendoDSi) 
FSK without an age limit
---
 Longplay uploaded on the 1st of May, 2016 and played by Evelyn Ch. :)
Rayman 1 for the Atari Jaguar © 1995 by Ubi Soft

THANKS A LOT TO:
My technical assistant...you know why :3
